title: Trendrick Lamaar 9/24: Elon Musk, The View, Harry Styles, Billie Eilish, Teen Wolf, Christopher Nolan
itunes:title: Trendrick Lamaar 9/24: Elon Musk, The View, Harry Styles, Billie Eilish, Teen Wolf, Christopher Nolan
description:
In this edition of Trendrick Lamaar, Jack and Miles discuss the tragic split between Grimes and Elon Musk, two hosts of 'the View' testing positive for COVID, Harry Styles stopping his concert to give a fan dating advice, Billie Eilish's shoe collab, Tyler Posey confirming a new 'Teen Wolf' movie is coming, and Christopher Nolan's demands of his new studio
